    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People newly admitted into some society, office, or position, often a novice or unpracticed person; it may carry the connotation of having been instructed in some secret knowledge. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
